msgstr "分心"

#. [skirmisher]: id=distract
#: data/campaigns/The_Rise_Of_Wesnoth/utils/trow-abilities.cfg:7
msgid ""
"Allies adjacent to this unit are not affected by enemy Zones of Control."
msgstr ""

#. [skirmisher]: id=distract
